e::Settled`\n- `cancel_match.rs`: `PHASE_WAITING` → `RoundPhase::Waiting`\n- `timeout_cancel.rs`: `PHASE_LOCKED` → `RoundPhase::Locked`\n\n**Verification**: `anchor build` succeeded (release + test profiles). `cargo test -p rng-shared` — 27 tests passed, 3 doc-tests correctly ignored."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":242,"cache_read_input_tokens":106691,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":242},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9c12a0c3-e927-48e5-aad8-631d6cf2e564","uuid":"bc5406e8-b063-4731-8d30-f7e635419571"}
